"You can add a category to the favourites list from the categories page."="您可以從類別頁面將類別新增到我的最愛清單。"
"You can add an author to the favourites list from the authors page."="您可以從作者頁面將作者新增到我的最愛清單。"
"You can add backgrounds to a playlist from the apply button on any background."="您可以從任何背景上的套用按鈕將背景新增到播放清單。"
"You can add backgrounds to this playlist and apply this to your desktop."="您可新增背景到此播放清單，並套用此到您的桌面。"
"You can also alter how this background appears."="您也可以變更此背景的顯示方式。"
"You can change the timeout or disable screensavers from the operating system screensavers control panel."="您可以從作業系統螢幕保護程式控制面板上，變更逾時或停用螢幕保護程式。"
"You can customise your background by applying effects to it when you have clicked on the image by selecting other pages on the open page."="當您點擊影像時，您可以通過在打開頁面上選擇其他頁面來自定義您的背景。"
"You can even create advanced animations using the powerful creator tool."="您還可以使用功能強大的創作者工具，建立進階的動畫。"
"-You can record video from games or other applications by pressing WIN + G to access the XBox Game Bar.  WIN + ALT + R will start and stop a recording automatically of the currently focused application or game."="-您可從遊戲或其他應用程式錄製影片，只要按WIN + G即可存取 XBox Game Bar。  WIN + ALT + R將自動開始和停止錄製最近的焦點應用程式或遊戲。"
"You generated a new wallpaper but haven't saved it. "="您已產生新桌布，但尚未儲存。 "
"You have selected multiple backgrounds and are in random mode.  You can disable this by selecting a single background."="您已選取多個背景，目前處於隨機模式。您可以透過選取單一背景來停用此模式。"
"You have selected multiple backgrounds and are in random mode.  You can disable this by selecting a single background.\n\nAdjust settings using the button below."="您已選取多個背景，目前處於隨機模式。您可以透過選取單一背景來停用此模式。\n\n使用下方按鈕調整設定。"
"You have selected the random backgrounds folder so are in random mode.  You can disable this by selecting a different folder and can add to this by right clicking on backgrounds and picking the add to random option."="您已選取隨機背景資料夾，因此處於隨機模式。您可以透過選取不同的資料夾來停用此模式，並可透過在背景上按一下右鍵並挑選「新增至隨機」選項來加入內容。"
"You must give this combined effect a name"="您必須為這個合併效果命名"
"Your screensaver has been applied"="已套用您的螢幕保護程式"
"Your trial period has expired\nPlease purchase DeskScapes 8 to continue using it."="您的試用期已到期\n請購買 DeskScapes 8 以繼續使用。"

