"You have selected the random backgrounds folder which shows backgrounds in random order.  You can disable this by selecting a different folder and can add to this by right clicking on backgrounds and picking the add to random option."="您已選取隨機背景資料夾，該資料夾以隨機順序顯示背景。  選取不同的資料夾即可停用此功能，並且可以按背景右鍵並挑選新增到隨機選項來加入到此功能。"
